{"type":"message","id":"d292fe0d","parentId":"56605470","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:20:10.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The self-learning has been completed successfully. The notes have been saved to the memory file. Let me provide a brief summary of what was done.","thinkingSignature":"3e9fbbe6780647f45130a6cf985035ad207f7875bb15a1c48f60d29f1ca71941"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<final>\n✅ 自主学习已完成（空闲检测触发，无活跃对话）\n\n**已搜索并整理3个领域的最新动态：**\n1. **企业数字化转型**：国家200亿专项资金+地方量化目标（广东4000家规上企业转型）\n2. **智能安防与弱电工程**：AIoT融合+数字孪生普及，市场规模预计2030年破1.4万亿\n3. **IT运维与网络集成**：AIOps向Agentic演进、NaaS加速普及（30%中大型企业将采用）\n\n**已保存至**：`memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**综合洞察**：道简网络在智能安防高速增长+数字化转型补贴双重利好下，应重点关注AI预判安防产品、运维服务化升级、NaaS网络集成三大方向。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4862,"output":203,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49046,"cost":{"input":0.0014586,"output":0.00024359999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00302163}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775082004356}}
